The school previously known as "International House Xian" was officially disaffiliated by [[International House World Organisation]] in February 2019 and no longer has the right to trade under this name.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ihworld.com/school/profile/ih_xian |title=International House Profile |publisher=IHworld.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30}}</ref>

